### ==========================================
### ERROR SCENARIO EXAMPLES
### ==========================================

### 23. Missing Query (Should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/query
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "k": 5,
  "allow_adult": false
}

### 24. Empty Query (Should fail with 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/query
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "",
  "k": 5,
  "allow_adult": false
}

### 25. Large K Value (Should be capped at 50)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations/query
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "games",
  "k": 100,
  "allow_adult": false
}

### ==========================================
### SEARCH CONTROLLER INTEGRATION
### ==========================================

### 26. Traditional Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=action%20games&limit=5
Authorization: {{token}}

### 27. Search with RAG Enabled
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=action%20games&limit=5&useRag=true
Authorization: {{token}}

### 28. Search with Multiple Words
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=strategic%20turn-based%20rpg&limit=10&useRag=true
Authorization: {{token}}

### ==========================================
### NOTES
### ==========================================
###
### 1. Replace {{token}} with your actual JWT token
###    Format: Bearer <your-jwt-token-here>
###
### 2. Update {{baseUrl}} if using remote RAG service:
###    @baseUrl = https://bluocaroot-questro-rag.hf.space
###
### 3. Common HTTP Status Codes:
###    200 - Success
###    400 - Bad request (invalid parameters)
###    401 - Unauthorized (invalid/missing token)
###    503 - Service unavailable (RAG initializing)
###
### 4. Response includes:
###    - status: "success" or "error"
###    - query: echo of your query
###    - retrieved_items: ranked recommendations
###    - llm_response: generated explanation
###
### 5. First request after RAG restart may return 503
###    Retry after 5-10 seconds when service initializes
###
### ==========================================
